    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行与美联储的分歧引发了欧元滑向美元平价的讨论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/ecb-fed-split-ignites-talk-of-euro-sliding-to-dollar-parity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧洲央行决策者准备今年比美国央行采取更多降息措施，有关欧元与美元触及平价的讨论又重新出现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/ecb-fed-split-ignites-talk-of-euro-sliding-to-dollar-parity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行将在阿根廷单位出售中录得 10 亿美元税前损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/hsbc-to-book-1-billion-pretax-loss-on-sale-of-argentina-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司 (HSBC Holdings Plc) 同意出售其在阿根廷的业务，并将在第一季度从此次处置中记入 10 亿美元的费用，因为该银行将重点放在增长更快的亚洲市场上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/hsbc-to-book-1-billion-pretax-loss-on-sale-of-argentina-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 04:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者等待美国通胀数据，金价再创新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/gold-holds-record-high-as-investors-wait-for-us-inflation-print</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在下一组美国通胀数据公布之前，黄金将牛市延续至新纪录，这些数据可以为美联储下一步行动提供洞察。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/gold-holds-record-high-as-investors-wait-for-us-inflation-print</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 00:03:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀数据公布前债券上涨、股票下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的债券市场反弹，股市下跌，交易员们正在等待关键通胀数据，这将有助于塑造美联储下一步行动的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 22:13:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
